        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本帅，马超。我在张鲁王驾前为将。多蒙那蜀主刘璋，聘请前来，命俺镇守葭\n萌关等处。又命俺为帅，统领着大兵，前去攻打刘备，生禽张飞。也曾命探马\n前去，探听刘备的兵势。未见回报。\n来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四白龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伺候了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四白龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打探军情事，名为夜不收。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报，探子告进。与元帅叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打探哪路军情，一一讲来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有那刘备差来张飞，统领三千人马，前来攻打葭萌关，沿路而下，特来报知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探再报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。大胆张飞，本帅未曾发兵，他竟敢侵犯前来，岂肯容他猖狂。\n呔，众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四白龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起兵追敌去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四白龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂慢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟为何阻令？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，兄长，我想此事，何劳兄长出马，侍小弟出马会他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此马岱听令。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你带领人马前去，不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四白龙套引马岱同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看马岱此去，必然大获全胜。你等提防，掩门。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "马岱→马超",
