    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众人",
        "众将官",
        "劝你马前来屈膝",
        "四黑龙套",
        "张飞",
        "我兄弟三人战虎牢",
        "马岱",
        "马超"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四白龙套、马夫、马超同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼睹金角起，耳听好消息。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马岱上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见兄长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胜负如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大败而回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军家胜败，古之常理，下面歇息。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马岱",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢兄长。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马岱下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看马岱往日百战百胜，今日为何败阵？待本帅亲自出马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将官、众人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抬枪带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四黑龙套、马夫、张飞同上，会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来将通名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "翼德张！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张飞！来将？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你老爷马！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马超！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马超我的儿吓，还不下马归降？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一派胡言。众将官，"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "压住阵脚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言来怒气冲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四白龙套、四黑龙套同走十字号。张飞、马超同开打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "张飞小儿听端的：\n少若迟延命归西。"
        },
        {
          "character": "劝你马前来屈膝、张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听罢一言心头恼，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四白龙套、四黑龙套同走双出水。张飞、马超同开打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "马超我儿听根苗：\n挑吕布金盔无处逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我兄弟三人战虎牢、马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷不信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不信两下动枪刀，\n少时叫你命难逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞、马超同开打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，马超，敢是惧战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日天色已晚，明日再战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "各自收兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马超、马岱、马夫、四白龙套同下。张飞、四黑龙套、马夫同挖门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好枪法！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日气力不佳。众将官，今夜人不卸甲，马不可离鞍，提防偷营。下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四黑龙套同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺何不卸甲爽快爽快。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。张飞卸甲。马叫。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看我的战马乱跳。我不免刷洗刷洗。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞洗马，趟马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马吓马吓，明日阵前，你大叫一声，将马超吓下马来。奏与兄王，封你个马王！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞看枪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵呵。看这丈八枪，横眉门立目，待我取下来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞取枪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "枪吓枪吓，明日阵前，你将那马超挑下马来。奏与兄王，封你个枪元帅。"
