      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二太监引刘备同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，刘备。不知三弟胜负。\n来，三将军营盘去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。刘备、二太监同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二太监",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三将军不在营中，有盔甲在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。明白了。来，将盔甲带回。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
