        "马超"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明日与那马超交战便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急三枪〗。二黑龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马超讨战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二黑龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马超讨战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起过了。三军的，看盔甲过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盔甲不在营中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺与他赤身可以战得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可以战得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带马带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马超上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哼哼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张飞果不食信。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三军的，可是马超？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是马超。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞、马超同开打。马超败下，张飞追下。）"
        }
      ],
