      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马超单起霸上，张飞单起霸上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是惧战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日已晚，明日再战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家先收兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你家先收兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马超、张飞同开打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着，他不收兵，这便怎么处？有了，我吓他回去。\n马超，你敢夜战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马超",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吓。与你夜战。\n众将军，灯笼火把伺候！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四白龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四白龙套同拿灯上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦。他真点起。\n三军的，拿个亮来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四黑龙套同拿灯笼上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "灯笼火把来点起，"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫声孟起听一回："
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（张飞开打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么倒了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四黑龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "枪倒了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "张飞",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "颠倒丈八是怎的？\n少时叫你血染衣！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（三下锣。张飞、马超同开打，双收，同下。四白龙套、四黑龙套自两边分下。）"
        }
